<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jun1931"><font color="red">8 June 1931</font> <i>Unpublished</i> (to C.K. Ogden) [asking him to send a copy of the recording of Joyce's reading of Anna Livia Plurabelle to the Belfast musician Herbert Hughes, also asking him to destroy the recording of Sullivan singing Guillaume Tell("...I wrote to S. and got his permission. It is dreadful...")] </div>
